title: Matt Damon starrer `The Martian` grosses $118.5M offshore
text:
Matt Damon starrer `The Martian` grosses $118.5M offshore 
Entertainment Industry News.Net (ANI) : Tuesday 13th October, 2015 
Seems like it was a good weekend for 'The Martian', as it has collected 118.5 million dollars offshore. 
Ridley Scott's sci-fi drama starring Matt Damon bowed in 52 countries and now has a worldwide gross of 345.2 million dollars, reports Deadline.com. 
Meanwhile, Hugh Jackman starrer 'Pan' sailed into 52 countries this weekend and now has a worldwide cume of 40.5 million dollars. (ANI) More Entertainment Industry News   "Shaandaar" alongside Alia   Clinton 'shouldn't
